<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ecommerce Admin</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans&display=swap');
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat&display=swap');

      *{
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
      }

      img {
        max-width: 100%;
      }

      .login-logo {
        width: 15%;
        align-self: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      body {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100vh;
      }
      main {
        width: 70%;
        margin: 20px auto;
      }

      .image {
        height: 200px;
        background-size: cover;
        background-position-x: center;
        background-position-y: center;
        background-image: url(https://www.assignmentexpert.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hardest-programming-language.png);
        border: 1px solid rgb(218, 218, 218);
        border-bottom: none;
        box-shadow: 3px 0 5px rgb(226, 225, 225);
      }

      .texto {
        padding: 40px 50px;
        text-align: center;
        border: 1px solid rgb(218, 218, 218);
        border-top: none;
        box-shadow: 3px 3px 5px rgb(226, 225, 225);
      }

      .texto h1 {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        font-weight: 800;
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        color: #0F606B;
        font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      }

      .address {
        width: 100%;
        background-color: rgb(211, 211, 211);
        margin: 20px 0;
        padding: 10px 0;
      }

      .products {
        border: 1px solid rgb(185, 185, 185);
        margin-top: 10px;
        padding: 10px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .products .images {
        display: flex;
        width: 30%;
      }

      .images img {
        width: 100px;
      }

      .products p {
        width: 70%;
        text-align: left;
        padding-left: 30px;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .total {
        margin-top: 20px;
        text-align: right;
        font-weight: 800;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main>
    <img class="login-logo" src="http://localhost:8080/logo/logo-color.png" alt="Logotipo Geeky" />
    <section class="image">
    </section>
    <section class="texto">
      <h1>Pedido {{ user._id }}</h1>
      <p>¡Gracias por realizar tu pedido con Geeky! Aquí tienes un resumen:</p>
      <div class="address">
        <p>{{ user.firstName }} {{ user.lastName}} </p>
        <p>{{ user.address }}, {{ user.flat }}, {{ user.city }} ({{ user.province }}, {{ user.country }}) </p>
        <p>Teléfono de contacto: {{ user.tel }}</p>
      </div>
      {{#each user.cart}}
      <div class="products">
        <div class="images">
          {{#each this.images}}
          <img src="http://localhost:8080/images/{{ this }}">
          {{/each}}
        </div>
        <p><strong>{{ this.title }} - Cantidad: {{ this.items }} artículos</strong></p>
      </div>
      {{/each}}
      <div class="total">Precio total: {{ user.totalPrice }} €</div>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>